node.text: Cali K9 Dog training is more than just obedience. It’s socialization behavior modification, agility and problem-solving technique. At the end of every class I always go through and questions and answers so I can walk people through common issues that are usually easily fixed through the Cali K9 training system, sometimes they just need to hear it from me. Just another fun Saturday doing what I love! 💙🐶#calik9 #dogtraining #Problemsolving

node.text: I am posting this video to show the development of my dog as he prepares to get ready for next year’s trials. These are the beginning phases of tracking and I admit I have been slacking on this portion of the sport but through consistency and repetition I will be where I need to be once competition season starts. I honestly love this dog and feel like he has super high potential to go far so it’s up to me to get off my lazy ass and maximize potential!! Let’s get it! 💪💪💪#calik9 #ipg #dogsport

node.title: Slash’s first time tracking for IGP Dog Sport.

If you are in the New York area please join me  with my partners @globalstrays for an amazing event and fundraiser!
